result.name: 2011-tarmac-marine-dredging-ltd-area-435-396-monitoring-report
result.notes: Monitoring survey undertaken by EMU on behalf of Tarmac Marine Dredging Ltd. The primary aim of the survey was to undertake a repeat monitoring survey of the Licence Areas 435/396 and adjacent Black Bream Nest areas. Subtidal Habitat Mapping from multibeam data. Ground truthing using drop down video.
result.title: 2011 Tarmac Marine Dredging Ltd Area 435/396 Monitoring Report
